<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="de">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title>Terminerinnerung</title>
    <style>
        body { font-family: Arial, sans-serif; background: #f5f5f5; margin: 0; padding: 0; }
        .wrapper { max-width: 560px; margin: 40px auto; background: #fff; border-radius: 6px; padding: 32px 40px; }
        h1 { font-size: 1.25rem; color: #1a1a1a; margin-top: 0; }
        .item { background: #f0f4ff; border-left: 4px solid #4f6ef7; border-radius: 4px; padding: 14px 18px; margin: 24px 0; }
        .item-date { font-size: 1.5rem; font-weight: bold; color: #4f6ef7; }
        .item-desc { font-size: 1rem; color: #333; margin-top: 6px; }
        .footer { font-size: 0.8rem; color: #999; margin-top: 32px; }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
<div class="wrapper">
    <h1>Hallo {{ item.user.email }},</h1>
    <p>du hast einen bevorstehenden Termin in <strong>{{ item.reminderDays }} {{ item.reminderDays == 1 ? 'Tag' : 'Tagen' }}</strong>:</p>

    <div class="item">
        <div class="item-date">{{ item.date|date('d.m.Y') }}</div>
        <div class="item-desc">{{ item.description }}</div>
    </div>

    <p>Vergiss nicht, dich rechtzeitig vorzubereiten!</p>

    <div class="footer">Diese E-Mail wurde automatisch vom Micro Lab Kalender gesendet.</div>
</div>
</body>
</html>
